1 (13) As used in this subsection, "case" section:
2 (a) "Case" means a container holding twelve 750 ml bottles of
3 spirits or other containers containing spirits that are standard to
4 the industry.
5 (b) "Consumer Price Index" means the most comprehensive index
6 of consumer prices available for this state from the United States
7 Department of Labor, Bureau of Labor Statistics.
